These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
City: marseilles, london
2 different pets are kept: frog, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, may
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the person traveling to london is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| City   | london     | marseilles   |
| Pet         | rabbit | frog |
| Birthday     | august | may    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, brown
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, balloon-flower
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, pilot
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes red is the pilot##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Color   | brown | red  |
| Flower           | balloon-flower         | tulip     |
| Job     | electrician   | pilot    |

