1. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
2. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| City         | hamburg | miami    |
| Color         | azure         | coral        |
| Nationality   | indian         | egyptian    |

