.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
City: liverpool, marseilles
2 different games are played: go, mah-jongg
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, cooking
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, trike
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person driving the trike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| City      | marseilles     | liverpool |
| Game          | mah-jongg   | go  |
| Hobby         | card-games | cooking     |
| Transport   | motorbike  | trike         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-5::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, blend
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, colombian
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, azalea
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog
1. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
3. the colombian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Cigar      | ritmeester | blend       |
| Nationality           | colombian      | indian     |
| Flower   | azalea       | zinnia   |
| Pet           | frog          | chinchilla |

