2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, ritmeester
2 different pets are kept: cat, horse
2 different games are played: go, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the blend-smoker##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Birthday           | april | december    |
| Cigar   | blend       | ritmeester |
| Pet           | cat         | horse    |
| Game         | go    | mah-jongg   |

