.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-11::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, electronic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific
House: modern, townhouse
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, march
1. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Music-Genre           | soul | electronic |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | scientific      |
| House           | modern      | townhouse          |
| Birthday         | march | october       |

