The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, basketball
2 different pets are kept: frog, goat
There 2 different types of food: corn, kiwi
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
3. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Cigar    | dunhill | dannemann    |
| Sport         | basketball        | badminton |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| Food   | corn        | kiwi     |

 